---
import BaseLayout from '../components/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Services — Dmytro Klevakin"
  description="Cloud architecture, DevOps & automation, AI enablement, and coaching. Three engagement tiers — from a free discovery call to an embedded architect."
>
  <section class="page">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="div-label">Services</div>
      <h2>Three ways to work together.</h2>
      <p class="lead muted" style="margin-top:14px">
        Short engagements work best — a single review, a focused workshop, a 2-week scoping sprint.
        For deeper involvement let's chat first and shape it together.
      </p>

      <!-- 3-tier pricing -->
      <div class="tiers" style="margin-top:48px">

        <!-- Tier 1: Free -->
        <div class="tier">
          <div class="tier-badge">Free</div>
          <div class="tier-price">$0</div>
          <h3 class="tier-title">Discovery Call</h3>
          <p class="tier-desc">
            30 minutes to understand your problem. I'll tell you honestly if I can help — and what the smallest useful next step is.
          </p>
          <ul class="tier-list">
            <li>Cloud or DevOps challenge framing</li>
            <li>Honest assessment of your options</li>
            <li>No sales pitch, no obligation</li>
          </ul>
          <a class="btn ghost" href="https://calendly.com/dklevakin" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="margin-top:auto">
            Book a 30-min call →
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Tier 2: Architecture Review (featured) -->
        <div class="tier featured">
          <div class="tier-badge">Most popular</div>
          <div class="tier-price">$8k</div>
          <h3 class="tier-title">Architecture Review</h3>
          <p class="tier-desc">
            A 2-week deep dive into your architecture — I assess risks, document findings, and hand you a prioritised action plan you can act on immediately.
          </p>
          <ul class="tier-list">
            <li>Cloud architecture review (Azure / AWS / GCP)</li>
            <li>CI/CD &amp; DevOps maturity assessment</li>
            <li>Security &amp; compliance gap analysis</li>
            <li>FinOps &amp; cost-optimization report</li>
            <li>Written findings + 90-min readout call</li>
          </ul>
          <a class="btn gold" href="mailto:kl.dmitri@gmail.com?subject=Architecture+Review+enquiry" style="margin-top:auto">
            Start a review →
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Tier 3: Embedded Architect -->
        <div class="tier">
          <div class="tier-badge">Custom</div>
          <div class="tier-price">Let's talk</div>
          <h3 class="tier-title">Embedded Architect</h3>
          <p class="tier-desc">
            Part-time fractional CTA for teams that need ongoing cloud leadership without a full-time hire.
          </p>
          <ul class="tier-list">
            <li>Weekly architecture office hours</li>
            <li>Review PRs, ADRs, and RFCs</li>
            <li>Hiring &amp; team mentoring support</li>
            <li>Flexible scope — 1 to 6 months</li>
          </ul>
          <a class="btn ghost" href="mailto:kl.dmitri@gmail.com?subject=Embedded+Architect+enquiry" style="margin-top:auto">
            Send a note →
          </a>
        </div>

      </div>

      <!-- Service detail grid -->
      <div class="div-label" style="margin-top:72px">What I cover</div>
      <div class="svc">
        <div class="s">
          <div class="ico">CL</div>
          <h3>Cloud architecture</h3>
          <p>Azure-first, multi-cloud aware. I'll help you choose, design and de-risk — using Well-Architected and Cloud Adoption frameworks as the backbone.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Architecture review (1–2 weeks)</li>
            <li>Landing zone &amp; tenant design (Azure / AWS / GCP)</li>
            <li>Migration roadmap &amp; cost-optimization (FinOps)</li>
            <li>ASR &amp; backup strategies for on-prem → cloud</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="s">
          <div class="ico">DO</div>
          <h3>DevOps &amp; automation</h3>
          <p>Pipelines that survive Mondays. ARM, Bicep, Terraform, Ansible. Azure DevOps and GitHub Actions, with the boring quality gates that actually catch things.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>CI/CD assessment &amp; redesign</li>
            <li>IaC modules (Terraform / Bicep / ARM)</li>
            <li>SonarQube · Artifactory · Ansible integration</li>
            <li>Internal developer platform setup</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="s">
          <div class="ico">AI</div>
          <h3>AI &amp; vibe coding</h3>
          <p>How to actually use Claude / Copilot in day-to-day engineering, where to deploy custom skills, and how to ship faster without losing taste.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>AI workflow audit for engineering teams</li>
            <li>Custom Claude / MCP skills tailored to your stack</li>
            <li>Internal AI tooling (RAG over docs, code Q&amp;A)</li>
            <li>Hands-on enablement workshop</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="s">
          <div class="ico">CO</div>
          <h3>Coaching &amp; mentoring</h3>
          <p>Some architecture problems are people problems. As a certified NLP Master Practitioner and professional coach, I work with leads and architects on the human layer.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>1:1 coaching for Cloud / DevOps leads</li>
            <li>Career-path mentoring (engineer → architect)</li>
            <li>Team workshops on technical decision making</li>
            <li>Interviewer / hiring-process coaching</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="svc-cta">
        <div>
          <h3>Not sure which one fits?</h3>
          <p>Send a paragraph about what you're working on. I'll suggest the smallest possible engagement that actually helps.</p>
        </div>
        <a class="btn gold" href="mailto:kl.dmitri@gmail.com">Write me an email →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* ── 3-tier pricing ── */
  .tiers {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 16px;
    align-items: stretch;
  }
  @media (max-width: 820px) { .tiers { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

  .tier {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: var(--r-lg);
    padding: 32px 28px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
    transition: border-color 0.15s, transform 0.15s;
  }
  .tier:hover { border-color: var(--navy); transform: translateY(-2px); }

  /* Featured (middle) tier */
  .tier.featured {
    background: var(--navy);
    border-color: var(--navy);
    color: var(--paper);
    position: relative;
    transform: none;
  }
  .tier.featured:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); }

  .tier-badge {
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--gold-deep);
  }
  .tier.featured .tier-badge { color: var(--gold); }

  .tier-price {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: clamp(32px, 4vw, 44px);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    color: var(--navy);
  }
  .tier.featured .tier-price { color: var(--paper); }

  .tier-title {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: -0.015em;
    line-height: 1.2;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .tier.featured .tier-title { color: var(--paper); }

  .tier-desc {
    font-size: 14.5px;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.55;
    margin: 0;
  }
  .tier.featured .tier-desc { color: var(--muted-2); }

  .tier-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
    padding-top: 16px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
    flex: 1;
  }
  .tier.featured .tier-list { border-top-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.12); }
  .tier-list li {
    font-size: 13.5px;
    color: var(--ink);
    display: flex;
    gap: 10px;
    align-items: baseline;
    line-height: 1.45;
  }
  .tier.featured .tier-list li { color: var(--paper); opacity: 0.88; }
  .tier-list li::before {
    content: "";
    flex: 0 0 6px;
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--gold);
    transform: translateY(2px);
  }

  /* Override ghost btn in featured */
  .tier.featured .btn.ghost {
    border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.25);
    color: var(--paper);
  }
  .tier.featured .btn.ghost:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); }

  /* ── Service detail cards ── */
  .svc { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 14px; margin-top: 16px; }
  @media (max-width: 780px) { .svc { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
  .s {
    padding: 28px;
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: var(--r-lg);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 14px;
  }
  .ico {
    width: 40px; height: 40px; border-radius: 9px;
    background: var(--navy); color: var(--gold);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 15px; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: -0.04em;
  }
  .s h3 { font-size: 22px; font-family: var(--serif); font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: -0.015em; }
  .s p  { color: var(--muted); font-size: 14.5px; margin: 0; }
  .s ul {
    list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line); padding-top: 14px;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 6px;
  }
  .s ul li {
    font-size: 13.5px; color: var(--ink);
    display: flex; gap: 10px; align-items: baseline;
  }
  .s ul li::before {
    content: "";
    flex: 0 0 6px; width: 6px; height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%; background: var(--gold); transform: translateY(2px);
  }

  /* ── CTA strip ── */
  .svc-cta {
    margin-top: 34px;
    padding: 30px;
    background: var(--navy);
    color: var(--paper);
    border-radius: var(--r-lg);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 18px;
  }
  .svc-cta h3 { color: var(--paper); font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 24px; font-weight: 400; margin: 0; }
  .svc-cta p  { color: var(--muted-2); margin: 6px 0 0; font-size: 14.5px; max-width: 520px; }
</style>
